headline: Generac Gears Up to Report Q1 Earnings: Is a Beat in the Cards?
summary: GNRC's Q1 performance is likely to have gained from rising power outages, boosting sales of home standby and portable generators amid weakness in the C&I unit.

headline: Mean Green Introduces First Commercial-Electric Stand-On Autonomous Mower
summary: Mean Green, a leading battery-powered, commercial-grade turf care manufacturer and a Generac Power Systems (NYSE: GNRC) company, today announced the expansion of its commercial-grade electric mower lineup with its all-new Vanquish Autonomous.
